data.description: GOT A BIG FAMILY??? WELL LOOK NO FURTHER!! This home is IDEAL for multi-generational living with TWO (yes 2!) master suites downstairs & three (yes 3!) bedrooms upstairs! Upstairs also includes a room for a children's den, playroom or office (its current use) as well as a room that could be heated & cooled storage or a quiet area (it has no windows).  It is IDEAL for entertaining as the main floor has lots of living space with a formal dining room, great room & oversized eat-in kitchen.  With cooler days coming you can rock the day away on the wrap around front porch as well as enjoy the spacious deck out back.  In case you need more storage their is an oversized improved outbuilding in the backyard At this price & with all this square footage it is a GREAT buy at under $100 a square foot
